This is a shop app made using nodeJS along with ejs template engine in order to provide the views of different pages.
The features include:
Login and Signup
Sending mails when successful signup - using nodemailer
Forgot Password
Uploading images - using multer library
Making payments - using stripe library
Generating invoices - using pdfkit
and more...

Inorder to run the application:

1. Take clone of the repo
2. Make sure node is there in your system
3. Run command `npm i` into the directory
4. After the modules have been installed
5. Run command `npm start` to start app
